latestPosts.caption:
This bold masterpiece, brought to life by the masters of ink - Sunny Bhanushali (@sunnybhanushali)and Allan Gois (@allan_f_gois), is a stunning mix of art and meaning. 

The peaceful presence of Lord Buddha meets the strong energy of the dragon, expressing a story of balance and harmony. 

We’d say, every detail in this tattoo reflects perfection at its best. 

It is indeed a work of art that speaks to the heart, reminding us that true harmony comes from every part of our story!

[ aliens tattoo, aliens tattoo india, tattoos, throwback tattoo, collab tattoo, masters of ink, sunny bhanushali, allan gois, tattoo artist ]

When the masters of ink defined perfection, a true masterpiece was created. 

This bold backpiece, inked by @sunnybhanushali and @allan_f_gois, is a stunning blend of skill, passion, and artistry. 

With every stroke, they brought their mastery to life, creating a tattoo design that is as meaningful as it is breathtaking.

The calm presence of Buddha and the powerful energy of the dragon tell a story of balance, one of finding peace within strength. 

It is a reminder of life’s harmony, where both calm and chaos exist. This masterpiece is now a symbol of perfection, a true work of ink art that inspires beyond words.

latestPosts.caption:
This beautiful tattoo inked by @allan_f_gois and designed by @bhanupratap_101 is full of power.

At the top, there’s Zeus, a face of wisdom and strength, with every detail etched in art. 

And then stands an angel, graceful and bold, holding a sword, symbolizing protection and grace. 

Every detail, from the flowing robes to the detailed script in the background, adds depth and mystery, like pieces of a beautiful story etched in ink. 

Allan’s skill brings each element to life, making this tattoo a bold symbol of strength, courage, and artistry.
